meeting-recorder (0.3.0) noble; urgency=medium

  * Add a "Record now" button to the settings window for a manual recording,
    and a confirmed "Reset to defaults".
  * Simplify the settings window to the options that change the result; the
    remaining keys stay editable in config.json.
  * Collapse "Save" and "Save & Apply" into one Save that writes, restarts the
    service and closes the window — saving without restarting left the new
    settings inert.
  * Default stop_debounce_seconds to 60s: muting yourself releases the mic and
    used to end the recording. The extra wait is trimmed off the saved file.

 -- Md Salman Siddik <salmansiddik19@gmail.com>  Sun, 19 Jul 2026 15:30:00 +0600

