meeting-recorder (0.2.1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Fix the tray icon never appearing in the GNOME panel: it asked for
    `media-record`, which the Yaru theme does not ship, so gnome-shell drew an
    invisible icon. Prefer the symbolic names and fall back to the bundled
    hicolor icon.
